🧪 Task 7 – Production Lab

Imagine an application is consuming 100% CPU.

Investigate using:

top

or

ps aux --sort=-%cpu

Identify the process.

Find the PID.

Kill it safely:

kill PID

If it doesn't stop:

kill -9 PID

Verify it's gone:

ps -ef | grep process_name
